Titolo: Foul Play (video game)

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Foul Play is a 2013 brawler action-adventure developed by UK-based indie studio Mediatonic and published by Devolver Digital. It released for Microsoft Windows and Xbox 360 on 18 September 2013 and for OS X and Linux on 29 October 2013. After a port to PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita was announced in mid-2014, the PlayStation 4 received its version of the game on 1 September 2015 in North America as part of the PlayStation Heroes charity campaign.